    <string name="about_version_title">TRCardManager - About</string>
    <string name="about_version">Version</string>
    <string name="about_developer">XilvirSoft</string>
    <string name="about_application">\nThe application allows you to check the balance on your ticketrestaurant card in the same way that could be done on the web.\n
		It displays the current balance of the card, last 45 days movements and historical movements until 1 January of the previous year.\n
		To view more entries in the list, you only must drag the current list upwards and automatically more movements will be loaded.\n
		If you have the application open and make a payment, simply drag the list of movements down to load the recent payment.\n
		In the context menu you can also manage your card number and access password, you can also search restaurants or change application preferences.
		I hope this is useful and you can enjoy its use.\n\n</string>
